rows.label: tlk44310186_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I know we got orders to let anyone
and everyone enter the city, but...
I just can't get used to it.

rows.label: tlk44310186_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I can't help but be suspicious of
all these unfamiliar faces.

rows.label: tlk44310186_02_msg0003
rows.name:
How in the world do the other nations
keep public order...? I guess we'll have
to learn, and soon...
